headline.main: Rhode Island Police Take in Homeless Saxophonist for a Night
headline.print_headline: Rhode Island Police Take in Homeless Saxophonist for a Night

lead_paragraph: A homeless saxophonist was a guest of the Pawtucket Police Department in Rhode Island, although he didn't spend the night in a cell.
